Package com.linecorp.centraldogma.client

Interface Watcher<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the watch result type
    All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    public interface Watcher<T>
extends AutoCloseable
    Watches the changes of a repository or a file.
